===Etymology 1===
Cognate with {{och-l|怖}} ({{zh-ref|Wang, 1982}}; {{zh-ref|Schuessler, 2007}}). Compare {{cog|tbq-kuk-pro|*phoo(k/ŋ)||to startle; to alarm; to wake up}}, whence {{cog|lus|phâwk||to startle; to frighten}} (STEDT; {{zh-ref|Schuessler, 2007}}). Also compare {{cog|mkh-mnc-pro|*phiic||to be afraid}}, whence {{cog|mnw|ဖေက်||to fear}} ({{zh-ref|Schuessler, 2007}}).

